-- Ackman builds stake in Allergan, working with Valeant -sources 
-- By Svea Herbst-Bayliss and Olivia Oran
-- Mon Apr 21, 2014 04:54PM EDT
-- None



BOSTON, April 21 (Reuters) - Activist investor William Ackman has acquired a nearly 10 percent stake in wrinkle-treatment maker Allergan Inc  <AGN.N> and is working with Valeant Pharmaceuticals International <VRX.TO> to buy the company, sources said on Monday.

